Botswana to Maintain `Downward Crawl' on Pula to Boost Competitiveness

-- B y   J e r r y   B u n g u
-- 
2011-02-25T10:15:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/botswana-to-maintain-downward-crawl-on-pula-to-boost-competitiveness.html
Botswana will ensure a “modest
downward crawl” on its currency to boost the competitiveness of
exports as inflation remains above that of the country’s trading
partners, Bank of Botswana Governor Linah Mohohlo told reporters
in Gaborone, the capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jerry Bungu in Gaborone at 
